WEBVTT

00:01:35.890 --> 00:01:38.310
[Too Young To Love]

00:01:38.440 --> 00:01:41.259
[Episode 19]

00:01:43.900 --> 00:01:44.700
Lan!

00:01:46.180 --> 00:01:47.039
What happened?

00:01:49.630 --> 00:01:50.759
How are you feeling?

00:01:50.789 --> 00:01:51.910
I'm just feeling a bit...

00:01:51.910 --> 00:01:52.710
nauseous.

00:01:52.710 --> 00:01:53.360
Come on, slowly.

00:01:53.360 --> 00:01:54.360
Let me help you up.

00:01:55.310 --> 00:01:56.910
I'm a bit nauseous,

00:01:57.120 --> 00:01:58.720
and having a pain in the head.

00:01:58.910 --> 00:01:59.270
Is...

00:01:59.910 --> 00:02:01.170
your stomach hurting?

00:02:01.220 --> 00:02:02.190
Yes, it is.

00:02:04.630 --> 00:02:06.560
Put on my scarf. Don't catch a cold.

00:02:14.710 --> 00:02:15.500
That's a lot.

00:02:15.710 --> 00:02:17.310
How much longer will it take?

00:02:18.340 --> 00:02:20.400
The nurse said you would be on the drip

00:02:20.440 --> 00:02:21.770
till tomorrow morning.

00:02:23.020 --> 00:02:24.710
It's the flu season now.

00:02:24.990 --> 00:02:26.190
You should stay warm.

00:02:27.930 --> 00:02:30.329
Put it back on.
Or you might catch a cold too.

00:02:30.670 --> 00:02:31.300
I'm fine.

00:02:32.150 --> 00:02:33.410
Wait here for a second.

00:02:51.510 --> 00:02:53.329
You bought that many heat packs?

00:02:54.550 --> 00:02:55.150
Yes.

00:02:57.590 --> 00:02:58.840
With these,

00:02:59.110 --> 00:03:00.470
you won't feel cold anymore.

00:03:00.470 --> 00:03:00.980
Come on.

00:03:03.430 --> 00:03:05.150
I'm starting to sweat.

00:03:06.620 --> 00:03:07.990
That's the whole point.

00:03:08.110 --> 00:03:10.110
Sweating means you're recovering.

00:03:11.270 --> 00:03:13.000
There's a hot water bottle too.

00:03:13.150 --> 00:03:15.410
Your feet must be freezing, aren't they?

00:03:16.150 --> 00:03:17.579
Let it stay here for a while,

00:03:17.579 --> 00:03:19.040
and your feet will warm up.

00:03:19.990 --> 00:03:21.020
There's also water.

00:03:21.020 --> 00:03:22.220
It's a bit too hot now.

00:03:22.230 --> 00:03:23.560
Wait till it cools down.

00:03:23.870 --> 00:03:26.390
Tell me when you feel like drinking it.

00:03:26.390 --> 00:03:27.720
I'll pour you some then.

00:03:29.990 --> 00:03:31.780
Xiaole, you're so nice.

00:03:34.020 --> 00:03:35.550
You're treating me so well.

00:03:35.690 --> 00:03:36.990
I promise I'll repay you

00:03:36.990 --> 00:03:38.990
by treating you very, very well too.

00:03:39.040 --> 00:03:41.570
How do you repay me
when you're sick like this?

00:03:41.710 --> 00:03:42.310
Sleep now.

00:03:42.370 --> 00:03:43.130
Goodnight.

00:03:43.890 --> 00:03:44.760
Are you tired?

00:03:45.270 --> 00:03:46.710
How could I possibly be tired?

00:03:46.710 --> 00:03:48.150
But I think you are.

00:03:50.200 --> 00:03:50.930
How about...

00:03:51.300 --> 00:03:52.870
you sleep in the bed with me?

00:03:54.520 --> 00:03:55.850
I want to lean on you.

00:03:57.950 --> 00:03:58.710
Well then...

00:03:59.520 --> 00:04:00.550
fine.

00:04:05.450 --> 00:04:06.030
Easy.

00:04:06.300 --> 00:04:07.560
I'd hate to squish you.

00:04:13.740 --> 00:04:14.430
Your hand.

00:04:16.160 --> 00:04:17.750
Why does it feel so cold?

00:04:17.940 --> 00:04:18.430
Is it?

00:04:21.350 --> 00:04:22.050
Sleep now.

00:04:22.180 --> 00:04:24.440
You'll be well when you wake up tomorrow.

00:04:24.990 --> 00:04:25.550
Okay.

00:04:27.300 --> 00:04:29.870
My baby, go to sleep.

00:04:38.810 --> 00:04:39.700
Miss Luo,

00:04:40.110 --> 00:04:41.510
you had too much to drink.

00:04:41.550 --> 00:04:42.030
Come on.

00:04:42.470 --> 00:04:44.330
Get in my car. I'll drive you home.

00:04:44.590 --> 00:04:45.790
I can manage on my own.

00:04:47.430 --> 00:04:48.430
Just come with me.

00:05:21.470 --> 00:05:22.870
He must've overslept.

00:05:24.020 --> 00:05:25.700
The editor-in-chief will be back tomorrow.

00:05:25.700 --> 00:05:28.590
Haven't you long been interested
in the overseas division?

00:05:28.590 --> 00:05:30.470
I'll introduce you to him tomorrow.

00:05:30.470 --> 00:05:32.800
Remember, that's your only opportunity.

00:05:33.190 --> 00:05:34.210
Gosh, I'm screwed.

00:05:34.210 --> 00:05:35.750
I've screwed it all up.

00:05:39.430 --> 00:05:40.520
Hello, Xiaole.

00:05:41.350 --> 00:05:42.230
Ma.

00:05:42.790 --> 00:05:44.130
I...

00:05:44.370 --> 00:05:46.900
I don't think I can make it to the office
today.

00:05:47.110 --> 00:05:47.909
Xiaole,

00:05:48.110 --> 00:05:51.060
our editor-in-chief values integrity.

00:05:51.350 --> 00:05:52.440
If you stand him up this time,

00:05:52.440 --> 00:05:54.030
you'll hardly get another chance
to meet him.

00:05:54.030 --> 00:05:55.990
I-I know. I understand.

00:05:56.140 --> 00:05:57.380
But I'm afraid...

00:05:57.500 --> 00:05:59.159
I really can't arrive in time.

00:05:59.260 --> 00:06:00.270
Sorry.

00:06:00.700 --> 00:06:03.230
What's more important than your meeting
with the editor-in-chief?

00:06:03.230 --> 00:06:05.260
Others don't even have
such an opportunity.

00:06:05.260 --> 00:06:08.060
This could be a big break in your career.

00:06:08.090 --> 00:06:10.090
I know this is a great opportunity,

00:06:10.500 --> 00:06:12.700
and I deeply appreciate your help, Ma.

00:06:12.960 --> 00:06:13.770
However...

00:06:14.670 --> 00:06:17.270
I really need to attend to an emergency
at home.

00:06:18.500 --> 00:06:19.230
I'm sorry.

00:06:29.760 --> 00:06:31.530
I bought you breakfast.

00:06:32.330 --> 00:06:34.620
Steaming hot porridge.

00:06:35.790 --> 00:06:37.310
Have you eaten yet?

00:06:38.110 --> 00:06:38.790
Yes, I have.

00:06:42.909 --> 00:06:44.380
Come on, sit up. Careful.

00:06:48.550 --> 00:06:49.350
Slowly.

00:06:51.260 --> 00:06:51.920
Is it good?

00:06:55.240 --> 00:06:56.700
After you finish the porridge,

00:06:56.700 --> 00:06:57.940
I'll take you back to campus.

00:06:57.940 --> 00:07:00.870
You should spend the next couple days
resting in your dorm.

00:07:00.870 --> 00:07:02.590
Aren't you supposed to meet
the editor-in-chief this morning?

00:07:02.590 --> 00:07:03.590
I'm fine on my own.

00:07:03.590 --> 00:07:04.260
It's okay.

00:07:04.290 --> 00:07:05.380
Don't worry about me.

00:07:05.380 --> 00:07:06.240
I can handle it.

00:07:06.590 --> 00:07:08.590
No. I can go back to campus myself.

00:07:08.590 --> 00:07:09.650
It's time you left.

00:07:11.940 --> 00:07:13.070
I've got it all planned out.

00:07:13.070 --> 00:07:13.800
Don't worry.

00:07:13.910 --> 00:07:16.510
But this opportunity is very important
to you.

00:07:16.540 --> 00:07:17.750
Really, it's okay.

00:07:18.650 --> 00:07:19.850
We have already...

00:07:20.200 --> 00:07:21.170
rescheduled...

00:07:21.260 --> 00:07:22.100
the meeting.

00:07:22.620 --> 00:07:23.220
Is it true?

00:07:23.470 --> 00:07:24.200
True as told.

00:07:24.600 --> 00:07:25.680
I'll meet him another day.

00:07:25.680 --> 00:07:26.390
Good then.

00:07:26.660 --> 00:07:27.180
Eat up.

00:07:28.450 --> 00:07:29.050
Is it good?

00:07:29.170 --> 00:07:29.610
Yeah.

00:07:29.870 --> 00:07:31.400
I feel like I'm alive again.

00:07:32.390 --> 00:07:32.790
[Lutao Free Restaurant]

00:07:32.790 --> 00:07:34.390
You've been waiting, right?

00:07:36.470 --> 00:07:37.670
Did you get rained on?

00:07:46.030 --> 00:07:50.340
[Lutao Free Restaurant]

00:07:52.960 --> 00:07:54.050
Such heavy rain.

00:07:54.510 --> 00:07:56.140
How about a drink at my place

00:07:56.310 --> 00:07:57.440
till the rain stops?

00:07:59.620 --> 00:08:00.280
Okay. Let me

00:08:00.290 --> 00:08:02.150
give you a ride then. I drove here.

00:08:02.440 --> 00:08:02.990
Yu,

00:08:03.300 --> 00:08:04.700
go home and get some rest.

00:08:05.840 --> 00:08:07.100
Okay, I'm leaving now.

00:08:15.180 --> 00:08:16.510
What are you doing here?

00:08:16.790 --> 00:08:19.850
The forecast said it would rain,
so I came to pick you up.

00:08:27.030 --> 00:08:28.030
Where's the rain?

00:08:28.670 --> 00:08:30.930
It'll be raining soon. Do you believe it?

00:08:30.990 --> 00:08:31.750
Let's go.

00:08:40.960 --> 00:08:44.240
[U-turn permitted
at the intersection ahead]

00:08:49.260 --> 00:08:51.020
This is the fifth New Year

00:08:51.050 --> 00:08:52.810
we've spent together.

00:08:57.800 --> 00:08:59.370
Time is really...

00:09:00.020 --> 00:09:00.890
flying.

00:09:01.410 --> 00:09:02.170
Yeah.

00:09:07.510 --> 00:09:08.030
Come on.

00:09:08.460 --> 00:09:09.460
Let's celebrate.

00:09:12.990 --> 00:09:13.850
Happy New Year.

00:09:14.070 --> 00:09:15.070
Happy New Year.

00:09:21.480 --> 00:09:22.360
I...

00:09:24.690 --> 00:09:25.480
have

00:09:25.750 --> 00:09:27.160
something to ask of you.

00:09:27.920 --> 00:09:28.520
What is it?

00:09:34.720 --> 00:09:35.720
Move in with me.

00:09:36.870 --> 00:09:37.810
What?

00:09:38.480 --> 00:09:39.280
I'd love to...

00:09:39.890 --> 00:09:41.370
see you every morning

00:09:41.600 --> 00:09:42.580
when I wake up.

00:09:44.800 --> 00:09:45.560
I mean it.

00:09:49.240 --> 00:09:50.060
Wait a second.

00:09:51.270 --> 00:09:52.240
Why?

00:09:52.480 --> 00:09:54.680
I need to give you something important.

00:09:57.240 --> 00:09:57.830
Rings.

00:10:00.720 --> 00:10:01.850
Let me put one on you.

00:10:07.510 --> 00:10:08.360
Agreed?

00:10:10.000 --> 00:10:11.730
It just slipped onto my finger.

00:10:13.000 --> 00:10:13.360
Yes.

00:10:14.390 --> 00:10:16.320
That ring just obeyed my order.

00:10:20.480 --> 00:10:21.240
Fireworks!

00:10:25.600 --> 00:10:26.530
No one's around.

00:10:29.360 --> 00:10:31.530
Come here.
Let me help you put on the gloves.

00:10:31.530 --> 00:10:32.810
It's a bit cold today.

00:10:33.960 --> 00:10:36.090
We single people are so jealous of you.

00:10:36.480 --> 00:10:37.480
Where is Zhao Zhenghao?

00:10:37.480 --> 00:10:38.870
Why is he late every year?

00:10:38.870 --> 00:10:40.340
I'm here, aren't I?

00:10:41.390 --> 00:10:42.850
You missed me, didn't you?

00:10:43.270 --> 00:10:43.750
Look.

00:10:44.080 --> 00:10:45.510
What a load!

00:10:45.960 --> 00:10:48.420
Did you just empty
an entire fireworks shop?

00:10:50.270 --> 00:10:51.190
Where is Fan?

00:10:52.120 --> 00:10:53.350
How come he's even later than me?

00:10:53.350 --> 00:10:54.810
I'll call him and rush him.

00:10:54.960 --> 00:10:55.790
Don't.

00:10:56.080 --> 00:10:56.600
Just stand away.

00:10:56.600 --> 00:10:57.530
Ning, over here!

00:10:58.000 --> 00:10:58.630
Long time no see.

00:10:58.630 --> 00:10:59.200
Ning.

00:11:02.000 --> 00:11:02.860
What happened?

00:11:03.390 --> 00:11:05.120
Did Fan and Luo Ningzi break up?

00:11:05.120 --> 00:11:05.970
Shut up.

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:07.610
Are they picking sides now?

00:11:08.240 --> 00:11:10.040
It can't be that serious, right?

00:11:12.200 --> 00:11:13.530
Chen Fan and I will solve

00:11:13.600 --> 00:11:15.000
the problems between us.

00:11:15.470 --> 00:11:17.070
Let's set off the fireworks.

00:11:17.630 --> 00:11:21.610
Perhaps Chen Fan is too busy dealing with
his own business to come here.

00:11:21.750 --> 00:11:23.030
I doubt that.

00:11:23.360 --> 00:11:24.240
He puts

00:11:24.270 --> 00:11:26.550
romantic relationships above all things.

00:11:26.550 --> 00:11:28.950
A breakup is like the end of the world
to him.

00:11:29.450 --> 00:11:30.000
Alright.

00:11:30.030 --> 00:11:31.140
It's getting late.

00:11:31.160 --> 00:11:32.360
Let's set off the fireworks now.

00:11:32.360 --> 00:11:34.560
Or we'll miss the New Year's Eve dinner.

00:11:35.000 --> 00:11:35.530
Come on.

00:11:35.630 --> 00:11:36.890
Set off the fireworks.

00:11:37.120 --> 00:11:37.840
Here you are,

00:11:37.840 --> 00:11:38.430
Ning.

00:11:38.630 --> 00:11:39.020
Thanks.

00:11:39.020 --> 00:11:40.750
Put on some music to liven things up.

00:11:40.750 --> 00:11:41.390
Let me see.

00:11:44.750 --> 00:11:45.880
How about this song?

00:11:48.840 --> 00:11:51.570
I've heard it before.
It's viral on the internet.

00:11:52.180 --> 00:11:53.210
I think it's a creation

00:11:53.210 --> 00:11:53.510
♪ Dusk gently fell on the coastline ♪

00:11:53.510 --> 00:11:54.500
of...

00:11:54.600 --> 00:11:56.800
an independent band called the God of War.

00:11:56.800 --> 00:11:56.870
♪ The quietly passing breeze
gave the clouds a kiss ♪

00:11:56.870 --> 00:11:59.530
The singer's voice sounds
just like Chen Fan's.

00:11:59.600 --> 00:12:00.240
Yes, it does.

00:12:00.240 --> 00:12:01.480
♪ The Earth keeps spinning round ♪

00:12:01.480 --> 00:12:01.930
Has it ever occurred to you
that given Chen Fan's talent,

00:12:01.930 --> 00:12:03.650
♪ Painted with shades of romance ♪

00:12:04.150 --> 00:12:04.390
♪ That was the moment I met you ♪

00:12:04.390 --> 00:12:05.300
it's a piece of cake

00:12:05.300 --> 00:12:07.100
for him to write a song like this?

00:12:07.180 --> 00:12:09.600
♪ Even mountains and seas
can't separate us ♪

00:12:09.600 --> 00:12:10.630
I just realized

00:12:10.630 --> 00:12:11.160
♪ I wish I could turn into a bird
to explore the world for you ♪

00:12:11.160 --> 00:12:12.870
something came up at the place
of my part-time job.

00:12:12.870 --> 00:12:14.170
I need to hurry back there now.

00:12:14.170 --> 00:12:14.840
♪ The vast, boundless Milky Way ♪

00:12:14.840 --> 00:12:15.740
I'll call you in a few days.

00:12:15.740 --> 00:12:16.120
♪ Sings its tender serenade ♪

00:12:16.120 --> 00:12:16.980
Happy New Year.

00:12:17.560 --> 00:12:17.870
♪ I can't live a second without you ♪

00:12:17.870 --> 00:12:18.700
Ning...

00:12:19.750 --> 00:12:21.110
Stay safe!

00:12:21.110 --> 00:12:24.300
♪ Looking forward
to the next beautiful dream ♪

00:12:24.370 --> 00:12:25.690
♪ I just want to be with you ♪

00:12:26.060 --> 00:12:28.940
♪ To see the most romantic starry sky
together ♪

00:12:29.170 --> 00:12:29.350
[Super Hero Fan]

00:12:29.350 --> 00:12:33.430
♪ The evening breeze tells
heartfelt emotions ♪

00:12:33.830 --> 00:12:34.340
[Cai Yu] [Refuse] [Answer]

00:12:34.340 --> 00:12:35.980
♪ All the stars surround you ♪

00:12:36.000 --> 00:12:37.670
♪ The moon smiles at you ♪

00:12:37.700 --> 00:12:38.430
♪ I give you all the good things
in the world ♪

00:12:38.430 --> 00:12:38.740
[Super Hero Fan]

00:12:41.160 --> 00:12:42.720
♪ And the light in your eyes ♪

00:12:42.890 --> 00:12:44.980
♪ Shines like diamonds ♪

00:12:45.230 --> 00:12:48.030
♪ Drawing an exclamation mark
in my world ♪

00:12:48.150 --> 00:12:48.600
♪ The evening breeze embraces you ♪

00:12:48.600 --> 00:12:49.120
Alright.

00:12:49.120 --> 00:12:49.690
As usual,

00:12:49.700 --> 00:12:49.720
♪ And I run towards you ♪

00:12:49.720 --> 00:12:50.480
let's make wishes!

00:12:50.480 --> 00:12:51.500
I want a boyfriend!

00:12:51.500 --> 00:12:53.510
♪ I hear our passionate heartbeats ♪

00:12:53.510 --> 00:12:55.050
Why do you want a boyfriend again?

00:12:55.050 --> 00:12:56.400
♪ We borrow a dream ♪

00:12:56.500 --> 00:12:57.600
♪ To build a castle ♪

00:12:57.600 --> 00:12:58.990
I hope the ones I love will all stay

00:12:58.990 --> 00:12:59.750
♪ Every star is a romantic symbol ♪

00:12:59.750 --> 00:13:01.120
safe and healthy!

00:13:01.120 --> 00:13:01.400
That'll come true!

00:13:01.400 --> 00:13:02.390
♪ Let me find you ♪

00:13:02.390 --> 00:13:03.520
Xiaole, make a wish.

00:13:05.240 --> 00:13:07.370
Who is setting off fireworks up there?

00:13:08.480 --> 00:13:09.480
Why is Mr. Hu still

00:13:09.480 --> 00:13:11.440
patrolling during the New Year?

00:13:12.480 --> 00:13:14.270
-Time to run.
-Let's go.

00:13:16.080 --> 00:13:18.480
♪ Even mountains and seas
can't separate us ♪

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:19.370
Stop!

00:13:19.480 --> 00:13:19.530
Stop there!

00:13:19.530 --> 00:13:20.120
♪ I wish I could turn into a bird
to explore the world for you ♪

00:13:20.120 --> 00:13:21.660
Don't you dare run!

00:13:21.720 --> 00:13:23.070
They're going towards the canteen.

00:13:23.070 --> 00:13:24.620
♪ The vast, boundless Milky Way ♪

00:13:24.640 --> 00:13:26.370
♪ Sings its tender serenade ♪

00:13:26.460 --> 00:13:28.620
♪ I can't live a second without you ♪

00:13:30.010 --> 00:13:30.750
♪ Looking forward
to the next beautiful dream ♪

00:13:30.750 --> 00:13:33.410
What a shame that we didn't get to watch
the fireworks for a longer time.

00:13:33.410 --> 00:13:34.790
♪ I just want to be with you ♪

00:13:35.040 --> 00:13:36.080
♪ To see the most romantic starry sky
together ♪

00:13:36.080 --> 00:13:37.510
How did you get this?

00:13:37.630 --> 00:13:38.250
I stuffed it in my pocket
during the chaos.

00:13:38.250 --> 00:13:39.720
♪ The evening breeze tells
heartfelt emotions ♪

00:13:39.720 --> 00:13:42.100
You're so brilliant.

00:13:43.240 --> 00:13:44.880
♪ All the stars surround you ♪

00:13:44.900 --> 00:13:46.390
♪ The moon smiles at you ♪

00:13:46.390 --> 00:13:46.650
Let me put it here.

00:13:46.650 --> 00:13:49.830
♪ I give you all the good things
in the world ♪

00:13:49.840 --> 00:13:50.270
I'm too scared to light it. You do it.

00:13:50.270 --> 00:13:51.620
♪ And the light in your eyes ♪

00:13:51.620 --> 00:13:51.910
Step back, will you?

00:13:51.910 --> 00:13:52.530
♪ Shines like diamonds ♪

00:13:52.530 --> 00:13:53.290
Sure.

00:13:53.750 --> 00:13:54.290
-Stay back.
-Yes.

00:13:54.290 --> 00:13:57.090
♪ Drawing an exclamation mark
in my world ♪

00:13:57.220 --> 00:13:58.740
♪ The evening breeze embraces you ♪

00:13:58.800 --> 00:14:00.490
♪ And I run towards you ♪

00:14:00.540 --> 00:14:03.720
♪ I hear our passionate heartbeats ♪

00:14:03.720 --> 00:14:04.010
Make a wish! Make a wish now!

00:14:04.010 --> 00:14:05.380
♪ We borrow a dream ♪

00:14:05.470 --> 00:14:05.480
♪ To build a castle ♪

00:14:05.480 --> 00:14:06.080
Oh, right.

00:14:06.120 --> 00:14:07.000
It's time to make a wish.

00:14:07.000 --> 00:14:07.990
I wish for Tong Xiaole and Yi Lan
to be together for ever and ever!

00:14:07.990 --> 00:14:09.670
♪ Every star is a romantic symbol ♪

00:14:09.670 --> 00:14:10.450
Consider that little wish granted!

00:14:10.450 --> 00:14:12.870
♪ Let me find you ♪

00:14:13.840 --> 00:14:15.050
Happy New Year!

00:14:15.080 --> 00:14:17.240
Happy New Year!

00:14:28.080 --> 00:14:30.200
I can't believe
you came back for the fireworks.

00:14:30.200 --> 00:14:30.930
Cheapskate.

00:14:33.240 --> 00:14:35.270
These fireworks could be a fire hazard
here.

00:14:35.270 --> 00:14:37.080
I should be responsible for their disposal

00:14:37.080 --> 00:14:38.540
since I brought them here.

00:14:38.960 --> 00:14:40.880
You're as responsible as ever.

00:14:40.960 --> 00:14:42.560
And you're as pretty as ever.

00:14:46.550 --> 00:14:47.750
You do have a good eye.

00:14:50.120 --> 00:14:50.790
By the way,

00:14:52.000 --> 00:14:53.550
you just said

00:14:53.790 --> 00:14:55.320
you wanted a new boyfriend.

00:14:57.360 --> 00:14:58.840
Did anything happen?

00:14:59.720 --> 00:15:00.670
No.

00:15:01.240 --> 00:15:03.480
I just don't think
I dated the right person before.

00:15:03.480 --> 00:15:05.910
But in my opinion,

00:15:06.000 --> 00:15:07.720
one shouldn't stop pursuing true love

00:15:07.720 --> 00:15:09.240
just because of a bad romance.

00:15:09.240 --> 00:15:10.750
I still believe in love.

00:15:11.270 --> 00:15:12.200
Yeah, I agree.

00:15:13.000 --> 00:15:15.510
If you are to get into a relationship
with someone,

00:15:15.510 --> 00:15:17.360
you should definitely have
a lot of information

00:15:17.360 --> 00:15:18.420
of him or her first.

00:15:18.600 --> 00:15:18.840
Yeah.

00:15:18.840 --> 00:15:19.870
That's how it should work,

00:15:19.870 --> 00:15:20.390
right?

00:15:21.960 --> 00:15:23.480
You're making it sound so simple.

00:15:23.480 --> 00:15:25.000
Have you met your true love?

00:15:25.000 --> 00:15:25.450
Me?

00:15:25.480 --> 00:15:26.080
Yeah.

00:15:29.480 --> 00:15:31.210
Well, I'm just a natural giver.

00:15:31.840 --> 00:15:33.900
I would put whoever I'm dating first.

00:15:35.120 --> 00:15:35.910
However,

00:15:36.360 --> 00:15:38.360
that always makes me seem annoying.

00:15:38.600 --> 00:15:40.360
But I actually like men of your type.

00:15:40.360 --> 00:15:41.620
I think they're great.

00:15:41.870 --> 00:15:44.200
I'd love to have a considerate boyfriend.

00:15:48.000 --> 00:15:48.800
What's wrong?

00:15:49.320 --> 00:15:49.870
Give it to me.

00:15:49.870 --> 00:15:50.870
Don't get burned.

00:15:52.870 --> 00:15:54.470
You should've been careful.

00:15:55.630 --> 00:15:56.230
It's okay.

00:15:56.480 --> 00:15:58.210
I'll put a Band-Aid on it later.

00:16:00.080 --> 00:16:00.940
Zhao Zhenghao.

00:16:03.360 --> 00:16:04.490
Shall we try dating?

00:16:14.530 --> 00:16:17.930
Tong, you can't h-hold your liquor.

00:16:18.000 --> 00:16:19.240
Cut the crap.

00:16:19.240 --> 00:16:20.720
No, no, no. I mean...

00:16:20.720 --> 00:16:21.960
I did have drinks just now!

00:16:21.960 --> 00:16:22.750
You call that drinking?

00:16:22.750 --> 00:16:23.720
Keep it down, you guys.

00:16:23.720 --> 00:16:24.360
You...

00:16:24.360 --> 00:16:26.720
It's New Year's.
Why should we keep it down?

00:16:26.720 --> 00:16:28.640
I need one more drink!

00:16:29.050 --> 00:16:29.510
Hold on.

00:16:29.510 --> 00:16:31.510
Wait, I just remembered something.

00:16:32.510 --> 00:16:34.510
Steady. W-What now?

00:16:37.830 --> 00:16:38.600
Red envelopes.

00:16:38.600 --> 00:16:39.960
We're giving red envelopes too.

00:16:39.960 --> 00:16:41.820
-I have some to give as well.
-Son!

00:16:41.870 --> 00:16:42.480
My love!

00:16:42.480 --> 00:16:43.410
Thank you, Dad!

00:16:43.480 --> 00:16:44.120
We have some too.

00:16:44.120 --> 00:16:44.600
Here you are.

00:16:44.600 --> 00:16:45.720
Give them to the children.

00:16:45.720 --> 00:16:47.120
Thank you, Dad!

00:16:47.120 --> 00:16:47.750
Xiaole!

00:16:48.360 --> 00:16:49.730
Thank you, Uncle Dong.

00:16:50.000 --> 00:16:50.870
Be good.

00:16:50.870 --> 00:16:52.720
-Thank you, Uncle.
-Here you are.

00:16:52.720 --> 00:16:53.360
This is yours, Xiaole.

00:16:53.360 --> 00:16:54.780
Happy New...

00:16:54.870 --> 00:16:55.720
Year!

00:16:55.750 --> 00:16:56.870
My dear brother-in-law,

00:16:56.870 --> 00:16:58.750
will you give me your red envelopes?

00:16:58.750 --> 00:17:00.630
Who are you calling "brother-in-law"?

00:17:00.630 --> 00:17:02.360
If you call me "brother-in-law" every year

00:17:02.360 --> 00:17:03.080
from now on,

00:17:03.080 --> 00:17:05.000
I'll give you red envelopes each year.

00:17:05.000 --> 00:17:06.660
I have four red envelopes now!

00:17:08.589 --> 00:17:09.349
We've had it settled.

00:17:09.349 --> 00:17:10.349
The two of us will...

00:17:10.349 --> 00:17:12.010
w-w-will go for a drink later.

00:17:12.480 --> 00:17:13.690
"Brother-in-law"?

00:17:14.480 --> 00:17:16.400
So what should I call you now?

00:17:20.880 --> 00:17:22.130
[Lutao Free Restaurant]

00:17:23.510 --> 00:17:25.109
Isn't it simplicity itself?

00:17:25.579 --> 00:17:26.450
You just pick

00:17:26.589 --> 00:17:27.589
a school you like.

00:17:28.030 --> 00:17:29.430
Then I'll ask a professor

00:17:29.610 --> 00:17:31.680
to write you a recommendation letter.

00:17:31.680 --> 00:17:32.480
As for the tuition fees,

00:17:32.480 --> 00:17:34.850
my foundation will sponsor you.

00:17:38.440 --> 00:17:39.380
Mr. Guo,

00:17:40.030 --> 00:17:41.310
I mean...

00:17:42.000 --> 00:17:42.650
Can I

00:17:42.680 --> 00:17:44.480
take this money from you as a loan?

00:17:44.480 --> 00:17:46.310
I'll pay you back
when I return from abroad.

00:17:46.310 --> 00:17:48.240
We can even sign a contract on that.

00:17:49.260 --> 00:17:50.590
You are a smart girl.

00:17:50.750 --> 00:17:51.810
I bet you know

00:17:52.000 --> 00:17:53.840
how to seize an opportunity.

00:17:54.830 --> 00:17:56.270
What I'm offering you

00:17:56.400 --> 00:17:57.630
is not just money,

00:17:58.160 --> 00:17:59.530
but also a springboard

00:18:00.830 --> 00:18:01.840
that allows you

00:18:02.480 --> 00:18:03.750
to jump to a higher place

00:18:03.750 --> 00:18:04.810
and to see further.

00:18:13.030 --> 00:18:14.440
Drink it up.

00:18:25.640 --> 00:18:27.480
Let me do it.

00:18:32.920 --> 00:18:33.640
Miss Luo.

00:18:37.000 --> 00:18:37.980
Mr. Guo,

00:18:38.160 --> 00:18:38.640
please,

00:18:38.680 --> 00:18:40.290
consider the money a loan.

00:18:41.400 --> 00:18:42.920
I'd hate to owe you a favor

00:18:43.000 --> 00:18:44.330
for this money.

00:18:44.640 --> 00:18:46.350
I just love your personality.

00:18:47.000 --> 00:18:48.240
But you should know,

00:18:48.440 --> 00:18:49.640
there is no such thing as a free lunch

00:18:49.640 --> 00:18:51.160
in this world.

00:18:53.750 --> 00:18:54.700
Mr. Guo,

00:18:54.960 --> 00:18:55.650
just let her

00:18:55.680 --> 00:18:57.200
mull it over.

00:18:57.480 --> 00:18:58.260
Today,

00:18:58.480 --> 00:18:59.920
we're here to enjoy a nice dinner

00:18:59.920 --> 00:19:00.980
and some fine wine.

00:19:01.000 --> 00:19:02.900
Come on. Let's toast to Mr. Guo.

00:19:03.240 --> 00:19:04.350
Cheers, Miss Luo.

00:19:09.400 --> 00:19:11.730
You can really hold your liquor, Miss Luo.

00:19:12.000 --> 00:19:13.260
Let me fill your glass.

00:19:13.310 --> 00:19:14.480
I can't drink anymore.

00:19:14.480 --> 00:19:15.100
These are

00:19:15.120 --> 00:19:15.750
the two last glasses.

00:19:15.750 --> 00:19:16.680
Propose a toast.

00:19:17.510 --> 00:19:18.000
Cheers.

00:19:23.000 --> 00:19:24.530
A great drinker, isn't she?

00:19:25.100 --> 00:19:25.750
Not bad.

00:19:38.070 --> 00:19:39.000
Let's have more.

00:19:41.400 --> 00:19:42.060
Mr. Shang,

00:19:42.440 --> 00:19:43.290
a toast to you.

00:19:54.410 --> 00:19:54.820
[Hotel]

00:20:00.740 --> 00:20:01.070
[Lutao Free Restaurant]

00:20:01.070 --> 00:20:03.130
Quite a dedicated manager, isn't he?

00:20:03.840 --> 00:20:05.100
He's already waiting.

00:20:05.420 --> 00:20:06.550
Thanks for coming, everyone.

00:20:06.550 --> 00:20:07.340
Everything is set.

00:20:07.340 --> 00:20:07.620
Please come in.

00:20:07.620 --> 00:20:08.150
Let's go.

00:20:13.760 --> 00:20:14.760
This way, please.

00:20:15.550 --> 00:20:16.270
Everyone!

00:20:17.020 --> 00:20:18.460
Let's give a big round of applause

00:20:18.460 --> 00:20:20.340
to welcome this band, the God of War!

00:20:20.340 --> 00:20:21.920
Yu, give me a break.

00:20:23.780 --> 00:20:25.010
Whether your dreams

00:20:25.190 --> 00:20:27.180
will come true or not depends on tonight.

00:20:27.180 --> 00:20:28.150
If you miss it,

00:20:28.290 --> 00:20:29.690
you'll miss everything.

00:20:30.090 --> 00:20:30.820
Get a move on.

00:20:31.080 --> 00:20:31.670
I...

00:20:32.220 --> 00:20:33.170
I can't drink anymore.

00:20:33.170 --> 00:20:34.170
Just come with me.

00:20:35.680 --> 00:20:36.310
Come on.

00:20:36.620 --> 00:20:37.800
Stop resisting, alright?

00:20:37.800 --> 00:20:38.360
Let's go.

00:20:38.390 --> 00:20:39.150
No, I refuse.

00:20:40.240 --> 00:20:40.970
Move!

00:20:42.880 --> 00:20:43.660
Who is it?

00:20:49.000 --> 00:20:49.830
Mr. Wang.

00:20:50.650 --> 00:20:51.880
Mr. Wang!

00:20:52.290 --> 00:20:54.590
He's making a scene in public.
Kick him out!

00:20:54.590 --> 00:20:55.560
Cai Yu, you brat,

00:20:55.670 --> 00:20:57.220
causing me trouble again, aren't you?

00:20:57.220 --> 00:20:59.430
I went to great lengths
to invite Mr. Chen over.

00:20:59.430 --> 00:21:01.090
You must apologize to him now.

00:21:01.130 --> 00:21:01.690
Wait.

00:21:01.840 --> 00:21:02.630
I'm the one to apologize?

00:21:02.630 --> 00:21:03.750
Of course you are.

00:21:03.780 --> 00:21:06.010
Mr. Chen comes to watch your performance
every night.

00:21:06.010 --> 00:21:06.890
Frankly speaking,

00:21:06.890 --> 00:21:08.100
I wanted to replace you guys long ago.

00:21:08.100 --> 00:21:09.350
Yet Mr. Chen insisted that you stay.

00:21:09.350 --> 00:21:10.480
Now it's not too late

00:21:10.830 --> 00:21:11.760
to replace them.

00:21:12.270 --> 00:21:12.870
Cai Yu,

00:21:13.200 --> 00:21:13.780
get out.

00:21:14.710 --> 00:21:15.200
Now!

00:21:39.270 --> 00:21:40.200
I'm not leaving.

00:21:43.910 --> 00:21:45.760
[Hotel]

00:22:03.030 --> 00:22:11.200
[Lutao Free Restaurant]

00:22:35.140 --> 00:22:38.830
[Lutao Free Restaurant]

00:23:04.380 --> 00:23:04.480
[Lutao Free Restaurant]

00:23:04.480 --> 00:23:06.000
Hello, Professor Ye.

00:23:06.000 --> 00:23:06.980
Luo Ningzi.

00:23:08.030 --> 00:23:10.830
That overseas exchange program slot
is yours now.

00:23:10.960 --> 00:23:12.370
Tuition is waived,

00:23:12.750 --> 00:23:14.680
and there's a scholarship for you.

00:23:15.550 --> 00:23:16.610
Congratulations.

00:23:16.640 --> 00:23:18.170
Your hard work has paid off.

00:23:18.680 --> 00:23:20.880
Great job getting through this period.

00:23:31.740 --> 00:23:37.370
[Lutao Free Restaurant]

00:23:41.240 --> 00:23:42.000
As expected,

00:23:42.030 --> 00:23:44.760
cramming wouldn't
get me through the interview.

00:23:47.750 --> 00:23:49.400
I've always known Ning is amazing.

00:23:49.400 --> 00:23:51.250
She got that one and only
exchange program slot.

00:23:51.250 --> 00:23:52.650
She's really something.

00:23:54.120 --> 00:23:54.920
How about...

00:23:55.480 --> 00:23:56.740
we go study abroad too?

00:23:57.240 --> 00:24:00.500
I happen to want to pursue further studies
in photography.

00:24:01.640 --> 00:24:02.640
You'll go with me?

00:24:02.790 --> 00:24:03.270
Yeah.

00:24:04.480 --> 00:24:05.670
Let's go wherever

00:24:05.790 --> 00:24:06.590
you want to go.

00:24:06.750 --> 00:24:07.400
Okay?

00:24:07.790 --> 00:24:09.520
How very kind of you!

00:24:12.620 --> 00:24:12.860
[When the sun goes down,
it's time to drink]

00:24:12.860 --> 00:24:14.460
♪ All the stars surround you ♪

00:24:14.490 --> 00:24:16.160
♪ The moon smiles at you ♪

00:24:16.190 --> 00:24:19.360
♪ I give you all the good things
in the world ♪

00:24:19.800 --> 00:24:21.370
♪ And the light in your eyes ♪

00:24:21.430 --> 00:24:23.550
♪ Shines like diamonds ♪

00:24:23.800 --> 00:24:26.570
♪ Drawing an exclamation mark
in my world ♪

00:24:26.690 --> 00:24:28.210
♪ The evening breeze embraces you ♪

00:24:28.230 --> 00:24:29.980
♪ And I run towards you ♪

00:24:30.040 --> 00:24:33.330
♪ I hear our passionate heartbeats ♪

00:24:33.550 --> 00:24:35.020
♪ We borrow a dream ♪

00:24:35.040 --> 00:24:37.180
♪ To build a castle ♪

00:24:37.490 --> 00:24:39.910
♪ Every star is a romantic symbol ♪

00:24:39.960 --> 00:24:42.400
♪ Let me find you ♪

00:24:54.000 --> 00:24:55.440
Thank you for protecting me

00:24:55.440 --> 00:24:56.140
last time.

00:24:59.000 --> 00:25:00.210
I just happened to be there.

00:25:00.210 --> 00:25:01.270
It was a small favor.

00:25:01.270 --> 00:25:02.270
Don't mention it.

00:25:04.680 --> 00:25:06.210
You've changed quite a lot.

00:25:07.480 --> 00:25:08.440
In what way?

00:25:11.270 --> 00:25:12.160
I can't name it.

00:25:12.350 --> 00:25:13.370
But in general,

00:25:13.440 --> 00:25:15.170
you've changed for the better.

00:25:15.590 --> 00:25:16.850
It's all thanks to you.

00:25:16.960 --> 00:25:18.250
If it weren't for you,

00:25:19.510 --> 00:25:20.110
I wouldn't have been

00:25:20.110 --> 00:25:22.120
able to find my...

00:25:22.230 --> 00:25:23.050
life goal.

00:25:34.710 --> 00:25:36.110
Anyway,
seeing you're doing well in everything,

00:25:36.110 --> 00:25:37.160
I'm relieved.

00:25:37.960 --> 00:25:41.020
I heard you would study abroad soon.
Congratulations.

00:25:42.550 --> 00:25:43.300
Thank you.

00:25:43.980 --> 00:25:44.870
And I wish you

00:25:45.030 --> 00:25:45.880
all the best.

00:26:07.440 --> 00:26:08.090
Lan,

00:26:08.290 --> 00:26:09.800
I'm heading abroad soon.

00:26:09.920 --> 00:26:11.350
I didn't tell you earlier

00:26:11.350 --> 00:26:14.050
because I didn't want you
to get too sentimental.

00:26:14.050 --> 00:26:15.320
Take good care of yourself.

00:26:15.320 --> 00:26:16.580
I'll be back in no time.

00:26:24.250 --> 00:26:24.970
Chen Fan,

00:26:25.900 --> 00:26:26.490
I am...

00:26:26.680 --> 00:26:27.830
going abroad soon.

00:26:28.110 --> 00:26:29.350
When we met up the other day,

00:26:29.350 --> 00:26:31.460
there were things
I couldn't bring myself to say.

00:26:31.460 --> 00:26:33.850
But anyway, you're a really nice guy.

00:26:33.880 --> 00:26:35.340
I should've cherished...

00:26:36.590 --> 00:26:37.930
what we had before.

00:26:38.000 --> 00:26:39.260
I wish you all the best.

00:26:46.070 --> 00:26:46.790
Chen Fan,

00:26:47.710 --> 00:26:49.750
I am... going abroad soon.

00:26:49.920 --> 00:26:51.160
When we met up the other day,

00:26:51.160 --> 00:26:53.220
there were things
I couldn't bring myself to say.

00:26:53.220 --> 00:26:55.670
But anyway, you're a really nice guy.

00:26:55.830 --> 00:26:57.290
I should've cherished...

00:26:58.400 --> 00:26:59.670
what we had before.

00:26:59.700 --> 00:27:00.960
I wish you all the best.

00:27:03.680 --> 00:27:04.870
Okay, roger that.

00:27:07.440 --> 00:27:08.030
What now?

00:27:08.060 --> 00:27:08.990
Are you leaving?

00:27:09.350 --> 00:27:10.610
How about I see you off?

00:27:11.160 --> 00:27:11.590
Okay.

00:27:13.480 --> 00:27:15.440
I'm not sure
when we'll see each other again.

00:27:15.440 --> 00:27:16.570
I hope when we do,

00:27:16.600 --> 00:27:17.950
we'll still be friends.

00:27:20.680 --> 00:27:22.490
Does that message you just sent me

00:27:22.490 --> 00:27:24.490
mean you regret breaking up with me?

00:27:27.400 --> 00:27:30.600
Among all emotions,
regret is the most meaningless to me.

00:27:30.800 --> 00:27:31.740
But for what it's worth,

00:27:31.740 --> 00:27:32.880
you're a really nice person.

00:27:32.880 --> 00:27:35.150
We just didn't meet at the right time,

00:27:35.170 --> 00:27:36.970
and I didn't cherish you enough.

00:27:38.210 --> 00:27:40.620
My application
to be a self-funded exchange student

00:27:40.620 --> 00:27:42.100
has also been approved.

00:27:42.910 --> 00:27:44.520
I think I'm going to the same country

00:27:44.520 --> 00:27:46.120
as the one you're heading to.

00:27:48.950 --> 00:27:50.120
Yes, I admit

00:27:50.220 --> 00:27:51.350
that I was indeed...

00:27:51.880 --> 00:27:53.330
a bit immature in the past.

00:27:53.330 --> 00:27:54.900
Come to think about it, at that time,

00:27:54.900 --> 00:27:56.500
maybe what you really needed

00:27:57.320 --> 00:27:59.720
was someone who could fight alongside you.

00:28:00.490 --> 00:28:01.490
Over these years,

00:28:02.040 --> 00:28:03.050
I've been trying hard

00:28:03.050 --> 00:28:04.720
to prove myself.

00:28:05.770 --> 00:28:07.210
Now, I think I deserve...

00:28:09.260 --> 00:28:10.920
a second chance with you, do I?

00:28:16.950 --> 00:28:17.600
Well...

00:28:18.490 --> 00:28:21.150
Seems like we two international students

00:28:21.310 --> 00:28:22.070
will have to

00:28:22.160 --> 00:28:23.400
stick together abroad.